  console.log(
    '[FORWARDING TO]',
    `${proxyReq.protocol}//${proxyReq.getHeader('host')}${proxyReq.path}`
  );
});
```

***

### ✅ EXPECTED OUTPUT

    [FORWARDING TO] https://kmbld2c-optimus-uat.mykotaklife.com/api/quote/v1/quote/d2ckmbl/saveQuote

👉 **This is the exact proof that proxy works**

### ❌ If URL is wrong

| Symptom          | Fix                 |
| ---------------- | ------------------- |
| Missing `/api`   | Don’t use `rewrite` |
| Extra `/api/api` | Remove double path  |
| Wrong host       | Env variable issue  |

